Best show of the tour.... so far.  That was the word in the parking lot after the show.  Bob got carried away during Hell in a Bucket, do over.  What do yous want me to do, to do for yous to see yous though?

Clasic Byrne show.

Globe.
sound not so good, the vocals sound hollow sound not so good, the vocals sound hollow

Hey I was there ...what else is new... This was one  GRATEFUL feeling show...just perfect for N.J. anyway...It was hard in the day to visit the jersey shows and not feel completeley paranoid bout the security and such...but all in  all this was one fine show...out of the bunch they played for the run there  ..  I recall the  grateful Rainbow in the parking lot durring the run ..awsome  ...AWSOME... I have photos...wink wink...lol..They  (DEAD)  Really  gave  some  good--  no- no- no -- GRATEFUL SPACE for the  shows  this  is  prime...PEACE   GRATEFUL DAN
Ship of Fools First of all, this is a wonderful audience recording.  Second of all, SoF's guitar solo is an incredible burst of psychedelic inspiration from JG.  Very nice!
